                "comment": "Alagna was amazing! He's a great Spanish teacher who loves teaching his language. Be ready to complete homework for every class, it is apart of your final grade! There are 2 compositions, and 4 exams with 3 quiz's. Lots of grammar content but if you study (or took Spanish in highschool) you should be fine! ",
                "difficulty_rating": 2,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
                "comment": "Professor Alagna was enthusiastic and encouraging. He made a great effort to keep us engaged with the content during a semester that wasn&#39;t ideal.",
