            {
                "comment": "I was not a fan of the type of teaching style that was given. Expecting a 101 class to gain knowledge of a language very quickly is not acceptable and not fair. It is something new and shouldn't be thrown at us all at once. It is unfair for the students that didn't take any Spanish in high school and had to struggle catching up.",
                "difficulty_rating": 4,
                "quality_rating": 2
